spren Metal Count;

Order Day Manifest
    Sun, Mon, Tue
Conceal

Surge Pair Manifest
    Metal left;
    Metal right;
Conceal

SoulCast Metal sum_pair(Pair p) Manifest
    Ascend p.left + p.right;
Conceal

SoulCast Abyss main() Manifest
    Count c = 5;
    Day today = Mon;
    Pair p = Pair(10, 20);
    Metal[] nums = [1, 2, 3];

    Reveal(c);
    Reveal(today);
    Reveal(p.left);
    p.right = 99;
    Reveal(sum_pair(p));
    Reveal(nums[1]);
    nums[1] = 7;
    Reveal(nums[1]);
Conceal
